   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00050"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb167805" type="place">I Kärntnerring 12</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00049"/>Lieber Arthur.</salute></opener><p>Ich kann zu der Vorle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ung leider ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>olut nicht kommen, werde aber trachten, Sie
               näch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens zur <rs subtype="implied" ref="#pmb167789" type="place">Ordinations<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tunde</rs> zu treffen.</p><p>Grüßen Sie, bitte, <rs ref="#pmb2167" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Salten</hi></rs> und <rs ref="#pmb10863" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Richard</hi></rs> und<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t gegrüßt von Ihrem</p><closer><signed>Loris</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><date>Montag</date>.</dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
